headline.main: White House Weighs U.S. Biofuels Program Change, No Position Yet - Official
headline.print_headline: White House Weighs U.S. Biofuels Program Change, No Position Yet - Official

lead_paragraph: The Trump administration is reviewing the possibility of a key change to U.S. biofuels policy requested by oil refiners and Carl Icahn, the billionaire investor and special advisor on regulations to President Donald Trump, a White House official said on Monday.
